      Things happen
   =20
 =20
Meta Faces  Historic Stock Rout After Facebook Growth Stalled. PayPal Stock=
 Tumbles After Disappointing Earnings Guidance. Joe Biden=E2=80=99s nominee=
 for top Fed watchdog signals tough stance on banks. Biggest  Texas Bitcoin=
 Miner Shuts Down Ahead of Cold Blast. Pool of  Negative-Yielding Debt Is N=
ow the Least in Three Years.=C2=A0France Probes Orpea as =E2=80=98Gravedigg=
ers=E2=80=99 Book Sparks Outrage. How Miami became the most important city =
in America.=C2=A0Jeff Bezos=E2=80=99s New Superyacht to Force  Dismantling =
of Dutch Bridge.=C2=A0Giuliani=E2=80=99s  =E2=80=98Masked Singer=E2=80=99 C=
ameo Reportedly Prompts Walk Off.If you'd like to get=C2=A0Money=C2=A0Stuff=
=C2=A0in handy email form, right in your inbox, please=C2=A0subscribe at th=
is link. Or you can subscribe to Money Stuff and other great Bloomberg news=
letters here. Thanks![1] For my part I think that this is probably correct =
but also that Tesla has even more compelling counterarguments, the main one=
 being that the justification for JPMorgan to adjust the warrants on a merg=
er event =E2=80=94=C2=A0that a merger event would crush Tesla=E2=80=99s vol=
atility =E2=80=94=C2=A0was just manifestly untrue here. If=C2=A0JPMorgan ad=
justed the warrant strikes down for the =E2=80=9Cannouncement=E2=80=9D of a=
 =E2=80=9Cmerger,=E2=80=9D it had to adjust them back up for the =E2=80=9Ca=
bandonment=E2=80=9D of that =E2=80=9Cmerger,=E2=80=9D which it did, but in =
a comically stingy way that Tesla, I think correctly, objects to.[2] For my=
 part:  No he didn=E2=80=99t come on.[3] =E2=80=9CThe cube measures over a =
foot and a half on all sides and has a wall thickness of about a quarter in=
ch.=E2=80=9D My rough math suggests that if it was solid it would weigh mor=
e than two tons and be worth=C2=A0something like $150=C2=A0million.
