</table><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">One way to do fraud when you are pitch=
ing an investment is to lie about the investment. =E2=80=9COur thing has gu=
aranteed 20% monthly returns with no risk,=E2=80=9D you say, and then you s=
teal all the money. This is pretty common.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=
Another=C2=A0way to do fraud when you are pitching an investment is to lie =
about the=C2=A0<em>alternatives</em>. =E2=80=9CIf you put money in a bank o=
r the stock market it will all be stolen from you by vampires; only our thi=
ng can protect you from that.=E2=80=9D (Then you steal all the money.) This=
 is =E2=80=A6 also pretty common? A lot of financial frauds seem to appeal =
to people with a conspiratorial mind-set; they are happy to believe that th=
e regular system is stacked against them and they need to give their money =
to a scammer to protect themselves.=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I=
t probably will not surprise you much to learn that an alleged gold-coin-in=
vesting scam allegedly did both. Here=E2=80=99s a <a href=3D"https://link.m=
ail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/26586412.267618/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9=
uZXdzL3ByZXNzLXJlbGVhc2UvMjAyMi0xNw/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB07f56fa2" item=
prop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color=
: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; bord=
er-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #cc=
c;">U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission enforcement action</a> against =
Safeguard Metals LLC and its owner Jeffrey Santulan; from <a href=3D"https:=
//link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/26586412.267618/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2V=
jLmdvdi9saXRpZ2F0aW9uL2NvbXBsYWludHMvMjAyMi9jb21wLXByMjAyMi0xNy5wZGY/607f07=
ceef4b8524a319a23cBa20e9289" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope"=
 target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !importan=
t; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-st=
yle: solid; background-color: #ccc;">the complaint</a>:</p><blockquote><p s=
tyle=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Guided by scripts, some of which were prepared by =
Santulan, Safeguard sales agents made false and misleading statements to in=
vestors about the purported risks associated with the investors=E2=80=99 ex=
isting securities holdings at investment banks and brokerage firms. For exa=
mple, Safeguard=E2=80=99s sales agents stated that a =E2=80=9CMoney Market =
Reform Law=E2=80=9D allowed banks and brokerage firms to freeze retirement =
accounts in the event of a market downturn; that top financial experts in t=
he United States were saying that another recession was coming very soon; a=
nd that when that happened, the investors=E2=80=99 accounts would be frozen=
 and they would not be able to get any money out of their 401(k) plans or I=
ndividual Retirement Accounts (=E2=80=9CIRAs=E2=80=9D). These statements we=
re misleading because, among other things, the law that Safeguard reference=
d applied only to money market funds in rare circumstances and could not re=
sult in an individual=E2=80=99s entire account being frozen.</p></blockquot=
e><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Honestly if you were susceptible to Safeguar=
d=E2=80=99s pitch this is not very reassuring?</p><blockquote><p style=3D"m=
argin: 16px 0;"><strong>Scammer:</strong> A new law allows the government t=
o freeze your retirement accounts! Buy gold!</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;=
"><strong>You:</strong> Ooh that sounds bad.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;=
"><strong>The SEC:</strong> Actually that law only applies in rare circumst=
ances.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;"><strong>You:</strong>=C2=A0Somehow t=
hat sounds worse?</p></blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Really if al=
l they did was misrepresent the importance of <a href=3D"https://link.mail.=
bloombergbusiness.com/click/26586412.267618/aHR0cHM6Ly9pbnZlc3Rvci52YW5ndWF=
yZC5jb20vbXV0dWFsLWZ1bmRzL21vbmV5LW1hcmtldC1yZWZvcm0v/607f07ceef4b8524a319a=
23cBcce951de" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_bla=
nk" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-botto=
m-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; bac=
kground-color: #ccc;">money-market-fund reform</a> I feel like they=E2=80=
=99d have a decent defense? That would be a fun trial to do, like, the SEC =
puts you on trial for lying about the safety of the traditional financial s=
ystem, and you turn around and put the traditional financial system on tria=
l. Also though:</p><blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Safeguard and S=
antulan also allegedly misled investors about Safeguard=E2=80=99s commissio=
ns and markups on the coins, charging average markups of approximately 64% =
on its sales of silver coins, instead of the 4% to 33% markups that they di=
sclosed to investors. According to the complaint, Safeguard obtained approx=
imately $67 million from the sale of coins to more than 450 mostly elderly,=
 retail investors, and kept approximately $25.5 million in mark ups.</p></b=
lockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">And:</p><blockquote><p style=3D"marg=
in: 16px 0;">Safeguard=E2=80=99s sales agents, in calls to potential invest=
ors, lied about their investment experience and qualifications. For example=
, in a script provided to safeguard=E2=80=99s sales agents, an =E2=80=9Cope=
ner=E2=80=9D sales agent was directed to introduce a =E2=80=9Ccloser=E2=80=
=9D sales agent to the potential investor as a =E2=80=9Csenior representati=
ve [who] has been helping retirees/conservatives protect their wealth for o=
ver 17 years now, including back in =E2=80=9908. He actually specializes in=
 401k/IRAs and has far more expertise on your particular situation.=E2=80=
=9D None of Safeguard=E2=80=99s employees had experience remotely fitting t=
hat description.</p></blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">That=E2=80=99=
