 years mastering the complexities of market structure and making invisible =
incremental improvements, and then one day you get an entirely blank canvas=
 on which to make up a whole new market structure; if you=E2=80=99re a pers=
on who loves market structure this just has to be more fun than the increme=
ntal stuff.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">But of course the appeal is als=
o in very important part financial. <em>So much dumb stuff</em> happens in =
crypto, and if you are a smart intermediary that dumb stuff is your profit =
