-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; back=
ground-color: #ccc;"> new ways to take money from the dumb</a>. The returns=
 to smart are very high.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">There is a small t=
ension between these points. If you are intellectually ambitious you will w=
ant to build cool new stuff that has never been done before; you will want =
every day to be an adventure of discovery. The attraction of leaving tradit=
ional finance for crypto is that you have learned everything worth knowing =
about your corner of traditional market structure and now you want to learn=
 new things. In your corner of traditional market structure you were maxima=
lly smart, having learned from long experience in a competitive business. I=
n crypto you are ... very very smart, yes, with lots of relevant technologi=
cal and markets knowledge that you can apply in new contexts, but perhaps <=
em>imperfect</em>. You are doing=C2=A0new ambitious stuff. You might get a =
