ock is still positive compared with a year ago. But other top holdings incl=
uding streaming device maker Roku, crypto exchange Coinbase Global, and vir=
tual health-care provider Teladoc Health have tumbled.</p><p style=3D"margi=
n: 16px 0;">Say what you will about Wood=E2=80=94and in online forums, on m=
essage boards, and across social media, they pretty much say it all=E2=80=
=94<strong>few money managers have ever lost as much cash yet kept so many =
