ng personal brand in an increasingly dull industry, strongly held and intui=
tive arguments for why her thesis is still right, a history of past perform=
ance =E2=80=94=C2=A0but that doesn=E2=80=99t make it easy to replicate.=C2=
=A0</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Also I will say that in a world of meme=
